Name: Lucy's Namecard
Desc: Get by unlocking Lucy's Mindscape: Ironfist Overseer
Desc2:
A card with a Boar Thiren Overseer from Leaps and Bounds Express Services Co. printed on it.
This namecard has an exquisite texture and design from a Throne Quarter print shop. But currently its only use is in contacting the little boars roaming the Outer Ring for delivery.
